modName: Race Menu Presest with an included Simple UUNP body Preset
summary: Just a preset (and a folder with all my others for Racemenu)
descriptionHtml:
The main file is NMM friendly so you can install and uninstall it, be aware of the requirement's though and though it is a RACEMENU preset it is aimed also at UUNP as well as there is an included Bodyslide body preset which you do not have to use, you may however want to readjute the body sliders depending on what body you ARE using. 


 The optional file (original main file now moved to optional section) is ONLY for experienced users whom know there way around there game's file's and so it is not NMM friendly.
 Requires.

 UUNP preset included based on UUNP HDT and XPMSE skeleton

 Racemenu by expired6978
http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29624/?
 XPMSE skeleton by Groovetama
http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/68000/?
 BodySlide and Outfit Studio by Caliente
http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/49015/?
 True Eye's by Jimtownirish
http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/49963/?
 KS Hairdos renewal by Kalilies, Stealthic Chaos and Shocky
 YYMP makeup was used, I can no longer find it as sadly the author has taken if off the nexus.



 Not a requirement but I used the textures from the great follower mod Taibai by Azzozza for my own use since I took a liking to them, better eye shapes etc, a great follower mod as well though since I can not speak chinese subtitles are a necessity.
http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/75989/?


 This is only for advanced users, back up any folders before you copying into them. 

 There are many superior presets already on the nexus, these are strictly B grade and for you to tinker with but do with them anything you wish.

 See readme.
